        <title>使用Circle CI自动部署Vuepress博客</title>
        <link>https://srcrs.github.io/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8circle-ci%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2vuepress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
